English: You're Hungry! Go home for Lunch.
French: Tu as faim! Allez à la maison pour diner.
Pas de pêche ici! Roulez encore
Portuguese(pt_BR): Não pesque aqui! Jogue de novo

English: The pail tips over! Lose one fish.

Portuguese(pt_BR): O balde caiu! Perca um peixe

English: Catch two fish & throw one back
French: Pêchez deux poissons & jetez en un
Portuguese(pt_BR): Pesque um peixe e devolva um

English: Catch two fish. Throw one back.
